title: Indonesia social media user penetration 2017 to 2023
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Share of group, containing a total of 7 data points.
Overall Share of group has increased over the Year.
Share of group is slightly increasing from 2017 to 2020, and finally roughly constant from 2020 to 2023.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018_.
The highest Share of group, of value 37.0 was reached at Year 2023
Minimum Share of group about 28.0 was reached at Year 2017
